title: Fat-Pie Podcast #2
description:
WallerFM is a comedy sketch podcast thing from Fat-Pie. Everything is performed, written and improvised by David Firth and Christian Pickup.

Episode#2

We take you on a trip down memory lane with this nostalgia special, reliving those golden WallerFM moments that you all grew up with. Who can forget Claim To Fame? Where were you when Graham and Terry talked about headlocks? and what ever happened to The Eternal Night with Roger and Stevie? Find out on this fortnight&#039;s sparkling edition of WallerFM: The Fat-Pie Podcast.
